metadata.name: Metamorphosis
metadata.description:
Total time spent on Metamorphosis [23 hours]

2400 × 3000 px

I thought it would be fun to include real life merchandise as a prize. Whoever mints the most will receive a custom hoodie of Metamorphosis, and a signed print shipped to your chosen address. I will announce the winner 24 hours after the mint has ended on Twitter.
